Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水遁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水鮫彈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的忍術一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼連你也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說剛剛拜託了二位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是很不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的逃亡忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會回到村裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旗木卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫輪眼 vs 寫輪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要跟好色仙人一起去取材
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這不是普通的取材之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想採訪一位女性 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這就去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒空和好色仙人一起去取材
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要專心修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要請卡卡西老師教我很多忍術呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近很偏心啊 卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是覺得那招你學不來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人很漂亮的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想見見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是輕易就被好色仙人說服的小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可知道比千鳥更厲害的忍術呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 只好帶佐助去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就回去收拾行李
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色仙人不要走 等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 蠻可愛的小鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙眼睛還像從前那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫輪眼的真正繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須做好最糟糕的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪和我的忍術一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來除了鼬之外還有人有那樣的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是複製忍者卡卡西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到吃驚的是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在茶餐廳我還在想 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些可疑的傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是宇智波鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有霧隱的怪人 千柿鬼鮫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到連我的名字都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是霧忍“忍刀七人眾“之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把大刀是鮫肌 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說再不斬那小子和你交過手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還算值得我一削
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 鬼鮫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他交手的話 就沒完沒了了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說消耗太多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他忍者會趕來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了我們的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這裡不是為了受傷的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妨讓我們瞭解一下你們的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了找點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要找的 是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和鬼鮫不同 不會浪費太多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍術 水遁.水陣壁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施術的速度好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒看到他結印
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用右手的手裡劍做誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用水遁攻擊我的下路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞察力與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身 施術的速度太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水分身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好個複製忍者 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟能把我們村的忍術用到這個份上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下 紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個才是影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然引爆了影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的忍術 新的忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定小櫻開始要喜歡我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓卡卡西老師和佐助大吃一驚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:07:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙十三歲可就當上了暗部分隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他這麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他的實力遠不止這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為非宇智波一族的你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟把寫輪眼用到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你並不適合那雙眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的身體不屬於我們一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼宇智波被稱為最強的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你見識一下寫輪眼的真正實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 別看他的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個 別看他的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們絕對不要睜眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在看就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概只有寫輪眼才能對付這招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如果擁有寫輪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少可以對抗一下萬花筒寫輪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻無法破解這個特別的寫輪眼瞳術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻術月讀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要有相同血統
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並擁有寫輪眼的人才能應對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有血繼限界的你 能撐到何時呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月讀的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間 時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,品質 都在我的掌握之下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後的72小時裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直用刀子刺你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月讀的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間 時間 品質 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在我的掌握之下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這痛楚決不是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這痛楚在幻術之下依然存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的精神力量到底能支撐多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下71小時59分59秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 卡卡西 還不能睜眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說完話你就倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那個世界的三天裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實中只不過是一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不殺我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他來說只是舉手之勞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了那招精神居然還沒崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 鼬 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那招即使是你用多了也很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要找的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佐助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是第四代火影的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人 到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多年沒回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鳴人交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鳴人交給你監護
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代火影的判斷是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過事情可能變化得連你都無法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到底想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從大蛇丸離開村子後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就一直在監視他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我知道 總有一天他會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一開始我只監視大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他加入了某個組織
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有那個組織的情報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知道是由九名忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組成的名為曉的小組織
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最近也沒什麼大動作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直從事諜報工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是成員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們幾乎都是遭到通緝的S級罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而鼬也是其中一員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們聚到一起總不是做善事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡你也應該知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最近我監視的大蛇丸脫離了組織
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.85,0:16:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織的人以每兩人為一組單獨活動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集術之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾就是他們要找的其中之一嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這個可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是具有最強查克拉的妖魔之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人總有一天要小心翼翼地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是他的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起 你看著佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教他寫輪眼的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人在中忍考試開始前 交給我調教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.00,0:17:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要找的 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鳴人體內的九尾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始行動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在行動的應該不只你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織的名字 是曉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鮫 把卡卡西帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外兩個讓他們消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉剛力旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的蒼蘭猛獸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁特凱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一身什麼打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是奇珍異獸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西竟被弄成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看他的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會中幻術的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了對付卡卡西 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我研究過應對寫輪眼的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個睜開眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與寫輪眼戰鬥時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目光沒有相對就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 只要根據對方的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來判斷他的行動並加以對付
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 你說的也許有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到這點的只有你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據腳來掌握對方的行動是需要技巧的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在情況緊急 不能教你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 馬上習慣一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅 你先帶卡卡西去醫療班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯瑪 掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 在我安排的暗部增援趕到之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來做你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思 夠種
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鮫 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是來打仗的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 不能再繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易熱血沸騰起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是很有幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是去深山修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有個非常漂亮的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在拋媚眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 鳴人 很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒准比小櫻更可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去 修煉 然後睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.30,0:22:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:22:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.71,0:22:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不 自來也的桃花劫 鳴人的災難
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還修不修煉了
